node.text: This hot girl summer we don’t need any more heat 🥵 I got you guys with the right products from @zerofusshaircare 💖 Using their heatless hair care line, here are three days of the different hairstyles I usually do in between washes and how the products keep my hair looking beautiful and refreshed! I've been using these products ALL the time to help limit the heat I'm using and keep my hair as healthy as possible. I just took them to Hawaii this past weekend for vacation and my hair was sleek and had no frizz the entire time! Use my code BIRDYVIP15 for 15% of your entire purchase! https://zerofusshaircare.com

node.text: On this day I uploaded my first YouTube video not knowing what it would become. No words in this world can ever explain how much you guys mean to me and I can’t wait to have you all on this next chapter! Thank you from the bottom of my heart for supporting my dreams! The best is yet to come! SI SE PUEDE 👏🏼

node.text: I wish I could pause time to appreciate the moments a little longer 🥺🤍 Today we celebrate you and the beautiful happy soul that you are. I will never get tired of saying how proud I am of you and how much joy and happiness you’ve brought into my life. I will forever be grateful that God made me your mother and I can’t imagine my life without you. I promise to keep raising you into the beautiful girl that you are. So loving, kind and full of joy. Te amo mi princesa hermosa Feliz Cumpleaños 🎂
